headline: Seagate 32TB Capacities Now Shipping to Channel and Retail Partners Globally
summary: DUBAI, United Arab Emirates, January 12, 2026--Seagate Technology plc (NASDAQ: STX), a global leader in mass‑capacity data storage, is showcasing advanced storage solutions at Intersec 2026 that help power the transformation of AI-driven video analytics into searchable, decision‑ready intelligence. The edge-to-cloud portfolio is designed to help businesses unlock the full value of their data and make smarter, faster decisions.
